{"id":292783,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-合肥铜陵路街道办事处不签协议逼居民搬/","date":"2013-05-09T17:01:05Z","modified":"2013-05-09T17:01:05Z","title":"维权网 | 合肥铜陵路街道办事处不签协议逼居民搬迁（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员周维林报道）合肥市瑶海区铜陵路街道办事处借合肥市正在进行的轨道二号线建设，对位于长江路与肥东路丁字路口的合浦北村一号楼进行征收拆迁，并派不明人员在夜里对不愿在没有签订拆迁补偿安置协议就交房的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">104</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">105</span><span>的房主杨越、沈国芳两位年届七十的老夫妻进行砸门窗等骚扰，而老人则采取在门前堆起沙袋，装上摄像头，夜里保持高度警觉以应对。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据杨越、沈国芳两位老人反映，和浦北村一号楼位于合肥市轨道交通二号线的铜陵路站和东二环路站的中间，距两站距离皆有 一公里 之遥，故杨越和沈国芳老夫妻二人认为不在轨道交通二号线红线范围内，更对街道拆迁办不与房主达成拆迁补偿安置协议就要房主交房之行为不满。和浦北村一号楼的其他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">32</span><span>户房主在没有签订拆迁补偿安置协议的情形下交房搬离，房子也被拆掉门窗和屋顶。自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日午夜</span><span>开始，就有数名不明身份人员到门口砸门、砸窗，将房子的卷闸门砸坏，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>皆有这种情况：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>分</span><span>许竟然有两人到门口用木棍砸摄像头，用消防灭火器对房门及摄像头处猛喷。老人就此情况多次报警无果。为对付骚扰，杨越和沈国芳老人在门口台阶上效仿军事工事堆起沙袋，在门上安上摄像头和瞭望口，警惕地守卫自己的房屋。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>时许，瑶海区铜陵路街道办事处负责拆迁的官员到老人处谈拆迁事宜，老人因从事照相行业要求提供能够营业的房屋，结果被拒绝，而且官员仍旧坚持不签协议，不先提供补偿安置房屋就要老人搬迁交房。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>杨越、沈国芳老人对此非常愤怒，他们的女儿在军队当兵卫国，可他们老俩口却要不顾年老体衰，冒着风险保护自己的房屋不被侵犯。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-xyUFNkjlP_w/UYvDt0t8QWI/AAAAAAAAhrQ/O3bxVyK7TU8/s1600/%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E6%8C%81%E6%A3%8D%E7%A0%B8%E9%97%A8.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-xyUFNkjlP_w/UYvDt0t8QWI/AAAAAAAAhrQ/O3bxVyK7TU8/s320/%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%8E%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E6%8C%81%E6%A3%8D%E7%A0%B8%E9%97%A8.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nwUieMrcITk/UYvDgxnV74I/AAAAAAAAhq4/GS9cAyRpxTg/s1600/%E6%8B%86%E6%88%BF%E9%A1%B6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nwUieMrcITk/UYvDgxnV74I/AAAAAAAAhq4/GS9cAyRpxTg/s320/%E6%8B%86%E6%88%BF%E9%A1%B6.jpg\" width=\"224\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-xZQWT_tCXyQ/UYvDm0C13zI/AAAAAAAAhrI/fUs-PFfJtuc/s1600/%E7%A0%B8%E5%9D%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B7%E9%97%B8%E9%97%A8.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-xZQWT_tCXyQ/UYvDm0C13zI/AAAAAAAAhrI/fUs-PFfJtuc/s320/%E7%A0%B8%E5%9D%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%B7%E9%97%B8%E9%97%A8.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-qWwqfXxRJAA/UYvE3lSuU8I/AAAAAAAAhrk/QdjK062d7hw/s1600/%E6%9C%887%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E7%89%875+008.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-qWwqfXxRJAA/UYvE3lSuU8I/AAAAAAAAhrk/QdjK062d7hw/s320/%E6%9C%887%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E7%89%875+008.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" va